No, you're crazy.

02:34.600 --> 02:36.340
You don't know nothing, Philly.

02:36.340 --> 02:37.840
Philly!?

02:37.840 --> 02:39.330
[DOG BARKING]

02:47.820 --> 02:49.810
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

02:49.810 --> 02:51.810
[WOMAN GIGGLING SOFTLY]

03:46.700 --> 03:48.690
